item.title: Apache Related Event Calendars
item.description: Help wanted ¶ This page can probably just redirect to the events.apache.org website, would anything be missing if we do that? Calendar ¶ This calendar lists major events relating to The Apache Software Foundation and our many Apache projects. We also have an automated [listing of upcoming Apache-related Meetups][5] (smaller events) available. This Calendar is maintained by Apache Community Development volunteers (ComDev); to have your event listed considered for addition please mail dev@community.
